Package org.ogema.driver.homematic.config

Class ThermostatConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ogema.driver.homematic.config.DeviceConfigs
      • org.ogema.driver.homematic.config.ThermostatConfig
  • public class ThermostatConfig
extends DeviceConfigs
    This class provides a list of configurations, that are supported by a type of device. The list key is the unique name of the configuration. For each physical instance of the device the list is cloned and fulfilled with the data provided by the physical device.
